863
00:59:50,117 --> 00:59:52,417
Capitão Deadpool...

864
00:59:54,287 --> 00:59:55,454
Não, só...

865
00:59:55,455 --> 00:59:57,205
-Só Deadpool, é.
-Só Deadpool.

